We did not test the robustness of clustering results because we did not
 incorporate genetic marker maps into our analysis.
 To compare the significance of the differences between experiments, we
 first looked at the distribution of the log-ratios of the read scores.
 The distribution of log-ratios across microarrays is often assumed to be
 normally distributed (even if it isn't) 
